1164
01:07:37.678 --> 01:07:41.223
POTS stands for postural orthostatic
tachycardia syndrome.

1165
01:07:41.724 --> 01:07:44.643
It's a blood pressure disorder.

1166
01:07:44.727 --> 01:07:49.523
You can either get dizzy. lightheadedness.
you can black out.

1167
01:07:49.607 --> 01:07:52.485
With POTS. you just black out.

1168
01:07:52.568 --> 01:07:54.320
It can happen very fast.

1169
01:07:54.403 --> 01:07:57.656
If I move a certain way.
it just comes out of nowhere.

1170
01:07:57.740 --> 01:08:00.910
I could just be sitting like this.
and it could hit me.

1171
01:08:03.079 --> 01:08:05.748
You can move the microphone.
It goes side to side.

1172
01:08:05.831 --> 01:08:06.832
