We were dressed as Playboi Carti.
That's his makeup that he does onstage.

1377
01:19:25.594 --> 01:19:28.138
And I think most people my age know that.

1378
01:19:28.221 --> 01:19:32.017
Her and Dom loved Carti.
Like. her and Dom really loved Carti.

1379
01:19:33.268 --> 01:19:35.812
That is what these kids do.
Everything's on social media.

1380
01:19:35.896 --> 01:19:38.273
They make crazy videos all the time. so…

1381
01:19:38.774 --> 01:19:40.609
-Um…
-[music fades]

1382
01:19:40.692 --> 01:19:45.280
Uh. if she didn't kill someone.
I guess it wouldn't have been a big deal.

1383
01:19:45.864 --> 01:19:49.075
But she did. So now it just kinda
sheds light on who she was.

1384
01:19:50.410 --> 01:19:51.787
[tearfully] To the families

1385
01:19:52.746 --> 01:19:54.372
of Dom and Davion.

1386
01:19:54.873 --> 01:19:56.416
I'm so deeply sorry.

1387
01:19:56.917 --> 01:19:59.544
I hope one day you can see
how I'd never let this happen

1388
01:19:59.628 --> 01:20:01.296
or do it on purpose.

1389
01:20:01.379 --> 01:20:03.006
And I'm so sorry.

1390
01:20:03.507 --> 01:20:04.966
And to my family.

1391
01:20:05.050 --> 01:20:07.636
thank you for the support
and all the love you guys give.

1392
01:20:07.719 --> 01:20:10.430
Thank you for fighting for me.
I love you all so much.

1393
01:20:10.514 --> 01:20:12.641
All right. I'm done.
Thank you. Your Honor.

1394
01:20:12.724 --> 01:20:14.851
[ominous music playing]

1395
01:20:14.935 --> 01:20:18.104
That was the worst apology
I think I've ever heard in my life.

1396
01:20:18.188 --> 01:20:21.274
I know when someone's being fake or not.

1397
01:20:22.025 --> 01:20:25.153
And that was not… That was not real.

1398
01:20:31.827 --> 01:20:33.912
[judge] Hello. Could you start
