1399
01:20:33.995 --> 01:20:36.748
Hi. Your Honor. My name's Davyne Flanagan.

1400
01:20:36.832 --> 01:20:38.959
Um. Davion was my older brother.

1401
01:20:39.042 --> 01:20:43.380
Davion was not just a big brother to me.
but a role model in many ways.

1402
01:20:44.756 --> 01:20:48.885
He was the person I trusted the most
because he made me feel safe.

1403
01:20:48.969 --> 01:20:51.847
He was the one
who picked me up when I fell.

1404
01:20:51.930 --> 01:20:56.393
He was my best friend and the only person
that has stayed with me since I was born.

1405
