the longest possible sentence.

1406
01:21:00.397 --> 01:21:01.773
Thank you. Your Honor.

1407
01:21:05.902 --> 01:21:09.155
[Natalie] Your Honor. this was
a terrible. tragic. nightmare accident

1408
