about the two dead people.

1412
01:21:20.500 --> 01:21:21.501
Dominic. okay?

1413
01:21:21.585 --> 01:21:24.045
I'm asking you for leniency

1414
01:21:24.129 --> 01:21:27.090
because this was a tragic accident
that she does not remember.

1415
01:21:27.173 --> 01:21:29.509
And Do… Davion. we don't…

1416
01:21:30.010 --> 01:21:32.721
-He's a new friend. And I'm so sorry.
-[judge] What does that mean?

1417
01:21:32.804 --> 01:21:35.765
-His life is worth less?
-No. no. no. No.

1418
01:21:36.558 --> 01:21:39.019
No. God. no. Not at all.

1419
01:21:39.102 --> 01:21:40.645
I understand what it looks like.

1420
01:21:40.729 --> 01:21:44.399
I'm… I'm… I'm saying that it was
a tragic accident. She would never--

1421
01:21:44.482 --> 01:21:46.902
-[judge] We're gonna disagree on that.
-[Natalie] I understand.

1422
01:21:46.985 --> 01:21:49.446
-I'm so sorry. guys. I'm sorry.
-[judge] Thank you.

1423
01:21:49.529 --> 01:21:51.114
-[Natalie] I love you.
-Love you.

1424
01:21:53.867 --> 01:21:56.578
[judge] I understand
that the pain in this room

1425
01:21:56.661 --> 01:21:58.997
wants me to impose the harshest sentence.

1426
01:22:00.332 --> 01:22:03.627
But I don't believe that would be
the appropriate sentence

1427
01:22:03.710 --> 01:22:08.048
because I do believe that Mackenzie
will not be out in 15 years.

1428
01:22:09.799 --> 01:22:13.929
She's sentenced on count two.
the murder of Davion Flanagan.

1429
01:22:14.429 --> 01:22:15.972
15 years to life.

1430
01:22:16.473 --> 01:22:20.268
She's sentenced on count one.
the murder of Dominic Russo.

1431
01:22:20.352 --> 01:22:21.645
15 years to life.

1432
01:22:21.728 --> 01:22:25.649
to be served concurrent to each other
with credit for time served.

1433
01:22:26.316 --> 01:22:27.984
There's a very good likelihood. Mackenzie.

1434
01:22:28.068 --> 01:22:30.570
that you will spend
the rest of your life in prison.

1435
01:22:34.282 --> 01:22:37.494
[music intensifies]

1436
01:22:37.577 --> 01:22:39.871
-[Natalie] Love you. Kenz.
-[Mackenzie] Love you all.

1437
01:22:39.955 --> 01:22:41.122
[man] We know you're innocent.

1438
01:22:49.547 --> 01:22:50.423
[music fades]

1439
01:22:50.507 --> 01:22:51.549
[woman sobbing]

1440
01:22:52.676 --> 01:22:56.930
{\an8}We are just thankful
that we feel justice was served today.

1441
01:22:57.013 --> 01:23:02.102
{\an8}Um. there's not a day that goes by
that we don't miss our son.

1442
01:23:02.185 --> 01:23:04.437
{\an8}and justice was served for him today.

1443
01:23:04.521 --> 01:23:07.357
Um. but honestly. there's no winners here.

1444
01:23:07.857 --> 01:23:09.401
There's no winners here today.

1445
01:23:09.901 --> 01:23:10.986
[somber music playing]

1446
01:23:11.069 --> 01:23:16.366
[Tim] It matters to me
that Davion and Dominic's loved ones

1447
01:23:16.449 --> 01:23:20.829
feel that justice was provided.

1448
01:23:21.413 --> 01:23:24.040
and that Mackenzie was held accountable.

1449
01:23:24.708 --> 01:23:31.715
And she will sit in a cage for a long time
because of what she did.

1450
01:23:36.011 --> 01:23:37.012
[music fades]

1451
01:23:37.095 --> 01:23:40.098
It's really hard every day in here.

1452
01:23:40.181 --> 01:23:45.437
I try to wake up
and be the best person I can be every day.

1453
01:23:45.520 --> 01:23:47.063
stay out of trouble.

1454
01:23:47.147 --> 01:23:50.650
There's not a moment that doesn't pass
where I don't…

1455
01:23:52.235 --> 01:23:54.362
I don't think about them or

1456
01:23:55.447 --> 01:23:56.489
I don't

1457
01:23:57.282 --> 01:23:59.534
feel the pain in my chest that…

1458
01:24:00.160 --> 01:24:04.080
It's still like a void of losing them and…

1459
01:24:08.501 --> 01:24:09.335
[door slams]

1460
01:24:11.337 --> 01:24:13.715
[interviewer] Is there any last word
that you'd like to say?

1461
01:24:16.593 --> 01:24:18.470
Did I touch on that… the right…

1462
01:24:18.553 --> 01:24:20.638
Okay. so everything is. like… You think…

1463
01:24:21.139 --> 01:24:24.142
I don't wanna force anything
and just say too much

1464
01:24:24.225 --> 01:24:26.144
or sound crazy.

1465
01:24:27.395 --> 01:24:32.525
I just wanna just make sure
that I'm big on the…

1466
01:24:33.193 --> 01:24:34.194
the no intent.

1467
01:24:34.277 --> 01:24:37.614
There was no intent whatsoever there.

1468
01:24:38.615 --> 01:24:41.701
I have excessive amounts of remorse

1469
01:24:41.785 --> 01:24:46.623
for Dominic. Davion.
both of their families.

1470
01:24:47.457 --> 01:24:51.169
This was not intentional.
and I will do everything I can to

1471
01:24:52.253 --> 01:24:55.423
prove that to the world and the families.

1472
01:24:59.969 --> 01:25:01.054
And that's it.

1473
01:25:02.931 --> 01:25:04.808
I have the capacity for forgiveness.

1474
01:25:04.891 --> 01:25:07.018
I just wanna know the truth
of what happened that night.

1475
01:25:07.685 --> 01:25:09.854
And I would be eternally grateful

1476
01:25:09.938 --> 01:25:14.067
for her to actually tell us
how those last few moments were.

1477
01:25:14.150 --> 01:25:18.905
No matter how… damaging to her
they might be to say.

1478
01:25:18.988 --> 01:25:21.199
just to say the truth and let us know

1479
01:25:21.282 --> 01:25:24.244
and let us grieve properly
and have some closure.

1480
01:25:24.327 --> 01:25:26.329
[somber music playing]

1481
01:25:27.038 --> 01:25:30.125
[Natalie] <i>We're not done yet. okay?</i>
<i>And I can't talk about anything.</i>

1482
01:25:31.126 --> 01:25:36.214
<i>So just… have trust in…</i>
<i>have trust in us. please.</i>

1483
01:25:36.297 --> 01:25:40.677
<i>Okay? But I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.</i>

1484
01:25:44.639 --> 01:25:46.891
It's tragic. what happened
to those two boys.

1485
01:25:47.809 --> 01:25:50.145
But think if it was your kid.

1486
01:25:50.228 --> 01:25:51.688
What if Mackenzie was yours?

1487
01:25:52.522 --> 01:25:53.690
How would you feel?

1488
01:25:54.983 --> 01:25:56.901
I'm gonna fight for my daughter.

1489
01:25:57.652 --> 01:25:59.946
And we have ironclad evidence

1490
01:26:00.029 --> 01:26:03.867
that disputes what was said in the trial.

1491
01:26:04.576 --> 01:26:05.952
This is the freeway incident…

1492
01:26:08.037 --> 01:26:11.791
where Mackenzie was accused of threatening
to crash the car two weeks before.

1493
01:26:12.417 --> 01:26:17.338
These are text messages between Mackenzie
and Dom's mom. Christine Russo.

1494
01:26:17.422 --> 01:26:19.757
Mackenzie says. "Can you come get Dom?"

1495
01:26:19.841 --> 01:26:23.219
"He just grabbed my steering wheel.
trying to spin out my car and hurt me."

1496
01:26:23.845 --> 01:26:27.432
Christine says. "Hench is on the way.
Calm down for now. please."

1497
01:26:27.515 --> 01:26:30.351
And then Mackenzie says.
"To be honest. I can't calm down

1498
01:26:30.435 --> 01:26:32.061
when he just tried to end my life."

1499
01:26:33.271 --> 01:26:37.192
She never threatened to crash the car
two weeks before the car accident.

1500
01:26:37.275 --> 01:26:39.194
He did. He did.

1501
01:26:39.277 --> 01:26:41.654
It wasn't her. She never
threatened to do anything before.

1502
01:26:41.738 --> 01:26:45.283
So that removes that whole prior intent

1503
01:26:46.117 --> 01:26:47.577
from their story.

1504
01:26:47.660 --> 01:26:50.580
These messages are now part of an appeal

1505
01:26:50.663 --> 01:26:53.166
based on evidence
that was never brought into the trial.

1506
01:26:53.249 --> 01:26:57.170
Mackenzie Shirilla. who is in prison
for killing two people in a car crash.

1507
01:26:57.253 --> 01:26:58.713
is asking for a new trial.

1508
01:26:58.796 --> 01:27:00.924
[Natalie] <i>We're gonna fight. fight. fight.</i>

1509
01:27:01.424 --> 01:27:03.176
<i>If I have to drive to the White House…</i>

1510
01:27:03.676 --> 01:27:06.679
<i>I'll take it all the way</i>
<i>to the Supreme Court if I have to.</i>

1511
01:27:07.430 --> 01:27:09.641
There's the Free Mackenzie Facebook page
somebody started.

1512
01:27:09.724 --> 01:27:12.185
Thank you again.
whoever all these people are.

1513
01:27:12.268 --> 01:27:15.021
And all the YouTube videos
sharing all the information.

1514
01:27:15.104 --> 01:27:18.191
{\an8}It is very probable
