[man 1] Look at that face.
Someone's gotta pardon her.

1519
01:27:27.033 --> 01:27:29.369
{\an8}Mackenzie is too pretty for prison.

1520
01:27:29.452 --> 01:27:32.538
We're all in this together.
Get her the hell out of there.

1521
01:27:33.122 --> 01:27:35.792
[man 2] <i>Follow Free Mackenzie Shirilla</i>
<i>on Facebook.</i>

1522
01:27:37.252 --> 01:27:38.628
