Sit down. be quiet. and leave us alone.

1527
01:27:50.431 --> 01:27:52.517
If they were truly sorry.
I think they would do that.

1528
01:27:53.518 --> 01:27:55.645
She could get out at thirty…

1529
01:27:55.728 --> 01:27:58.147
-What? Thirty-two. thirty-three?
-Mm-hmm.

1530
01:27:58.231 --> 01:28:01.401
Yeah. and start a family
and live a happy life. you know?

1531
