where you can donate money

1549
01:29:21.731 --> 01:29:25.193
to a scholarship
that will go to a student in need.

1550
01:29:25.777 --> 01:29:29.739
[reporter] <i>The plan is to send at least</i>
<i>one person to barber school fully paid.</i>

1551
01:29:29.822 --> 01:29:32.450
<i>But if their GoFundMe campaign</i>
<i>raises enough money.</i>

1552
01:29:32.533 --> 01:29:35.578
<i>they'll be sending people to school</i>
<i>for years to come.</i>

1553
01:29:36.079 --> 01:29:39.874
[Scott] There is a handful of days
in those two and a half years

1554
01:29:40.666 --> 01:29:41.751
that I've been happy.

1555
01:29:41.834 --> 01:29:45.171
Like genuinely. really happy.

1556
01:29:45.880 --> 01:29:48.800
The day we handed out the scholarship
was one of those days.

1557
01:29:49.467 --> 01:29:50.718
Congratulations.

1558
01:29:51.260 --> 01:29:53.262
[man] Whoo!

1559
01:29:53.346 --> 01:29:56.933
It's just good to see that someone.
even if they're not Davion.

1560
